Curs: Form basic sentences

the boy = el niño
the girl = la niña
the man = el hombre
the woman = la mujer
the apple = la manzana
the bread = el pan
the water = el agua
the milk = la leche
a boy = un niño
a girl = una niña
I am José. = Yo soy José.
You are José. = Tú eres José.
He is José. = Él es José.
She is María. = Ella es María.
I eat bread.  = Yo como pan.
You eat bread. = Tú comes pan.
He eats bread. = Él come pan
She eats bread. = Ella come pan.
I drink water. = Yo bebo agua
You drink water. = Tú bebes agua.
He drinks water. = Él bebe agua.
She drinks water. = Ella bebe agua.
